# RDM Developments (rdmdev)

Corporate website for **RDM Developments (Pty) Ltd** — a building &
renovation contractor based in Pretoria East, Gauteng.

## Stack

- **Framework:** Laravel 11
- **Admin:** Filament v3
- **Frontend:** Blade + Tailwind CSS, Vite 5
- **DB:** MySQL 8.0 (production) / SQLite possible for local
- **PHP:** 8.3 in production container (see docker/Dockerfile)
- **Testing:** PHPUnit (via `phpunit/phpunit: ^10.5`)

## Key files

- `docker/Dockerfile` — production image (php:8.3-fpm-alpine + nginx + supervisor)
- `docker/entrypoint.sh` — boot script: waits for DB, runs migrations, warms caches
- `docker/install.sh` — one-shot server installer
- `docker-compose.prod.yml` — 3 services: app, db, scheduler
- `DEPLOY.md` — deployment guide
- `config/rdm.php` — brand/contact values consumed by views
- `resources/views/partials/footer.blade.php` — footer + legal entity name
- `resources/views/layouts/app.blade.php` — layout + JSON-LD schema
- `resources/views/components/rdm-logo.blade.php` — responsive PNG logo

## Brand / legal

- **Display name:** RDM Developments
- **Legal entity:** RDM Developments (Pty) Ltd (used in footer copyright + JSON-LD `legalName`)
- **Schema.org type:** `GeneralContractor`
- **Logo:** `public/images/rdmdev-logo-480.png` / `-960.png` (transparent PNG, use `<x-rdm-logo>`)

## Local dev (Laragon)

```powershell
cd c:\laragon\www\rdmdev
php artisan serve             # or rely on Laragon's auto vhost
npm run dev                   # Vite dev server
```

`http://rdmdev.test/` if Laragon vhost is configured; otherwise `http://localhost:8000/`.
